name: ChatDKG (OriginTrail)
description: [项目级] ChatDKG is an open framework for efficient search, access, and utilization of trusted knowledge with AI, based on OriginTrail Decentralized Knowledge Graph (DKG) and Knowledge Assets. The ChatDKG framework is designed as an open community project to explore a diverse range of possible applications.。来源: https://github.com/OriginTrail/ChatDKG

genes.title: 项目概述
genes.content:
ChatDKG is an open framework for efficient search, access, and utilization of trusted knowledge with AI, based on OriginTrail Decentralized Knowledge Graph (DKG) and Knowledge Assets. The ChatDKG framework is designed as an open community project to explore a diverse range of possible applications.

来源: https://github.com/OriginTrail/ChatDKG
